There was a tragedy in the squirrelly family today. The little baby of whom we all grew to love after my last post, was found dead today. Investigators (Jerry Funk & Myself) say the death was slow and very unfortunate. Most would have guessed it's death to be a horrid gorey death brought on by the 40lb, Russian Blue/Korat, Misty. Though this was definitly not the case today in the Funk household. Witness (me) was taking on her nightly routine in the bathroom when walking over to the toilet caught a glimps of what was Cute Little Squirrely Squirrels. "I found him drowned floating in the toilet, eyes half shut. If only I could have been there to come to it's rescue." Tonight there is silence within the walls where the family of Cute Little Squirrelly Squrirrels lies. "Surely his family must have heard his screams as the tragity was taking place." Says Mr. Funk. Tonight before I go rest I would like to say thank you to Cute Little Squirrelly Squirrels for the great times we shared and I hope you rest in peace in the afterlife and or are reborn into another fantastic squirrelly squirrel life where acorns grow a plenty on trees. Make sure if your able to, watch over your family and help guide them to great squirrelly bliss in their lifetime. You will be miss much by all Cute Little Squirrelly Squirrels. In Loving Memory Of Cute Little Squirrelly Squirrels...

Yup there is a family of squirrels living in my wall... and somehow one of them has been getting through the walls into the house. heres a picture of this distructive creature. 2 victums (Mr.Funk as well as Wanda) of the squirrel's wild nature have both experianced the baby Jumping out at them out of nowhere from somewhere high up. My interview with Mr. Funk went something like this... "I had just woke up and got my morning cup of coffee. I took a few sips relising like I do everymorning that the coffee is too hot to drink right away so I headed to my bedroom setting the cup of coffee on the dresser. I had a dance that evening, so I opend up my closet to get my dresspants out when that little shit jumped outta somewhere in my closet landing stright onto my head! Just when I think its gone... it pops out of somewhere else." Here are some pictures I captured from my incounter with the seemingly harmless but extreemly distructive baby squirrel.

I thought that I could swim through the air yesterday so I jumped off a parking structure on 5th ave. 
When I descended grimly glancing at the concrete, my final resting place I realized wide eyed and feeling quite wise why my mind always spat out lies... Somberly I finalized that lies are a figment or fragment of the time, only you can specialize in the pieces depicted in the making of matter.
Why do I bother... I wonder.
Sleeping blindly under the future poster child who'll take his last breath. 
Hammering in bits of my future.
I see no brotherhood in this light.
Fight to Live. LIve tO Dide. 
Underneath this scar from above.
In a fairytale where sleeping beauty never wakes up.
Im a bit frightful of things that can be delightful.
"Its only in (death/life) I find the will to live through the night."
Take your pick...

You are Photo Manipulated. One glance at you would
lead a casual observer to think you're a
perfectly average human being. But the second
glance might be a double take. You take the
world around you and twist it-- just slightly,
to your own tastes. Although you have the
ability to fit in with large groups, they're
likely to veiw you as 'the oddball.' There's
something about you people can't quite put
their finger on. Still, you're not truely
twisted- just sort of bent.

Your Birthdate: May 27
Your birth on the 27th day of the month (9 energy) adds a tone of selflessness and humanitarianism to your life path. Certainly, you are one who can work very well with people, but at the same time you need a good bit of time to be by yourself to rest and meditate. There is a very humanistic and philanthropic approach in most of things that you do. This birthday helps you be broadminded, tolerant, generous and very cooperative. You are the type of person who uses persuasion rather than force to achieve your ends. You tend to be very sensitive to others' needs and feelings, and you able to give much in the way of friendship without expecting a lot in return.
